{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSS","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CSS","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model\">CSS Object Model</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriedades</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS/paintWorklet\"><code>paintWorklet (Static property)</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS/escape\"><code>escape()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS/supports\"><code>supports()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a CSSOM</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><code><font face=\"Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif\">A interface&nbsp;</font><strong>CSS</strong></code>&nbsp;carrega métodos&nbsp;CSS-relacionados&nbsp;úteis. Nenhum objeto com essa interface foi implementado: Aqui&nbsp;só contém métodos estáticos e futuramente uma interface útil.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propriedades","title":"Propriedades","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>A interface&nbsp;CSS&nbsp;é a interface utilizada e nenhum objeto desse tipo pode ser criado: só métodos estáticos são definidos aqui.</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"métodos","title":"Métodos","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>A interface&nbsp;CSS&nbsp;é a interface utilizada e nenhum objeto desse tipo pode ser criado: só métodos estáticos são definidos aqui.</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"métodos_státicos","title":"Métodos státicos","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Nenhuma método estático herdado</em>.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"css.supports_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS/supports\"><code>CSS.supports()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Retorna um&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> indicando se o par&nbsp;<em>property-value</em>, ou a condição dada do parâmetro é suportada.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"css.escape_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS/escape\"><code>CSS.escape()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Pode ser usado para escapar um string mais usado como parte de um seletor CSS.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificações</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Estado</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/#the-css.escape%28%29-method\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM)<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'CSS' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Rascunho atual</span></td>\n   <td>Adicionado o &nbsp;&nbsp;<code>escape()</code> método estático.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-3/#the-css-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Conditional Rules Module Level&nbsp;3<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'CSS' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Candidata a Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>Definição inicial.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>28.0</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/22\" title=\"Released on 2013-06-25.\">22.0</a> (22.0) [1]</td>\n   <td>6.0</td>\n   <td>12.1</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>escape()</code><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td>46.0</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/31\" title=\"Released on 2014-07-22.\">31.0</a> (31.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n\n\n\n\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>22.0 (22.0)<sup>[1]</sup></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>12.1</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>escape()</code><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>31.0 (31.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Também disponível através do&nbsp;<code>layout.css.supports-rule.enabled</code>&nbsp;preferência desde&nbsp;Gecko 20.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Components.utils.importGlobalProperties\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Components.utils.importGlobalProperties</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Propriedades","id":"propriedades"},{"text":"Métodos","id":"métodos"},{"text":"Métodos státicos","id":"métodos_státicos"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"A interface CSS carrega métodos CSS-relacionados úteis. Nenhum objeto com essa interface foi implementado: Aqui só contém métodos estáticos e futuramente uma interface útil.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSS","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"CSS","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSS","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CSS","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CSS","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"CSS","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"CSS","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/css","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/css/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CSS","title":"CSS"}],"pageTitle":"CSS - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}